{"tid":1370172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邱騰華：《逃犯條例》修訂已是明日黃花","createTime":"2019-07-27T02:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T13:23:44.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":141,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"4009808e00b97f34d04724c4933f53d92926a8ce","tid":1370172,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:08:34.000Z","msg":"有公務員發聯署信呼籲政府成立調查委員會，商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華出席電台節目時指出，問責官員和公務員都一同為市民服務，難免對社會事件感受較大，每個人都有自己的看法，亦可能受情緒影響，完全可以理解，但相信所有公務員都會繼續緊守崗位。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華又表示，對近日的示威衝突感到很不開心，希望社會繼續堅持包容、守法的核心價值，行政長官林鄭月娥亦已經多次公開解釋停止修例，並用上很決絕的字眼，表明《逃犯條例》修訂已經是明日黃花，呼籲社會向前看，找機會坦誠相談。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2202271/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2202271%2F&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=79826ebd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2202271/</a>"},{"pid":"ba3199d44f09ca9bf240f392accd5b80a05781a7","tid":1370172,"uid":227788,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:10:12.000Z","msg":"一件垃圾 <br />\n佢仲想做特首？"},{"pid":"aa512bef710675f1064979ad4644ab1a398bc988","tid":1370172,"uid":127416,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"睇新聞學成語<br />\n<br />\n壽終正寢 明日黃花 殘花敗柳 頹垣敗瓦 ..."},{"pid":"ae8e7956c71792a96d527c4503efd3004a0d425d","tid":1370172,"uid":13754,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:10:42.000Z","msg":"林鄭已經係明日黃花，邱騰華你同佢一齊壽終正寢啦"},{"pid":"e5e08dd0ad9408794700d11ae4c018409ecd1334","tid":1370172,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa512bef710675f1064979ad4644ab1a398bc988","tid":1370172,"uid":127416,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"睇新聞學成語<br />\n<br />\n壽終正寢 明日黃花 殘花敗柳 頹垣敗瓦 ..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"